40:04.608 --> 40:07.543
-Stop it, Harper!
-I'm not doing anything.

40:14.718 --> 40:16.777
Stop it, Harper!

40:16.954 --> 40:20.515
-Mom!
-Harper! Stop it!

40:20.624 --> 40:23.115
You two are acting like little brats!

40:23.260 --> 40:28.357
