40:57.261 --> 41:00.719
Mom? Can I sleep with you?

41:00.831 --> 41:03.129
Yeah, honey. Come on.

41:04.835 --> 41:07.269
Right here. There we go.

41:34.665 --> 41:36.098
Oh, shit.

42:23.714 --> 42:26.808
-Hey! Okay, look, here's the deal.
-Hi.

42:26.917 --> 42:29.147
We had a fire in our garage.

42:29.252 --> 42:32.813
The good news, we started to rebuild it.

42:32.923 --> 42:35.824
The bad news, never finished it.

42:35.926 --> 42:39.987
So, right now, all it is,
