-Yeah.

01:01:09.736 --> 01:01:13.968
Well, you start by doing coke, and then
you move on to a little crystal meth,

01:01:14.073 --> 01:01:18.032
you get paranoid, then you find heroin,
and after that...

01:01:20.847 --> 01:01:23.213
